body_html: @qiaohaijun this is not a bug in TFTRT, it is a bug in your script that converts TFTRT model to serving model. As error mentions 'TitleLSTM/my_trt_op_2_native_segment' is not an OP but it is a function. It looks like your serving conversion script can't handle functions.
